Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 劫持巴士的恐怖分子所提出的要求是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 他们要求立即解散驻扎在阿尔泰的维和部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及释放监禁在我国戴斯普利特监狱里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待审判的凪·达伊·阿尔泰前大公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼中将 报告状况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被劫持的 是往返东部国土与首都的长途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质包括乘务员在内共10人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子在车内安装了炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁如不接受要求 将引爆炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正值总统选举
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦处理不善
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会影响选举结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责人员的是城市警察吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12分钟前 已由我国家安全保障局接手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 乙HiME部队已到达现场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只待阁下一声令下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有人质的情况下 不能轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须谨慎处理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务名「寂静海」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁静的大海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字取得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您过奖了 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能尽量“安静”些…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和往常一样出手…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她给逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该早就说过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种大小的石头已经对她不管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:01:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R1 待机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R2 待机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R3 待机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已锁定目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以开火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须避免不必要的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静的 冷静的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静 嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 波曼中将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将就由我们 安静地悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些卑鄙之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我把人质放了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正出来和我对决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿米蒂奇准将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将 把那些恐怖份子干掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈拉德队长 你也做些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我要冷静 冷静…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是伊梨娜·伍兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我听得很清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是便捷的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦宫·艾莉卡果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车型是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊？这群胆小鬼 快给我回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那疯女人是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister遥·阿米蒂奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克利斯德的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个破坏者阿米蒂奇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一个不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会大祸临头的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 那是我的点心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石上候选人访谈的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士劫持事件好像有了新的进展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把镜头转向那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不过来的话我就上了 恶棍们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢过来我就把所有乘客炸飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有种就引爆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有艾尔里斯灵魂之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会害怕区区一个炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从加尔德罗贝来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是这里的负责人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然当上Delta队长 你发达了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千绘·哈拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话和你说 非正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫神山消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是真白公主 连Meister舞衣也消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 您认识Meister舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉面店的那个女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说想开连锁店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就叫她把总店开在艾尔里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫她不听我的劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来 留言说“去寻找真白殿下”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister艾莉卡也跟着失去踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后她去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经锁定了她所搭乘的长途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 巴士…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这事件真的能解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经查清犯人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主谋嫌疑人 果然是前阿尔泰军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆军近卫队出身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在准将捣乱后 就一直处于僵持状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花市的事件也还在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又即将缔结「战略乙HiME限制交涉」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容有失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 要松饼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么镇静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你这么说 现在不是无计可施吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的工作不就是要打破这种僵局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行突破之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算放任不管 事态还是会有所发展的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且连舞斗服都没有就想强行突破…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉·加拉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成乙HiME的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和有没有舞斗服无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 重要的是气魄对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占领巴士的各位恐怖份子先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下届大总统最有力候选人石上 石上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现众人的期盼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦多尔·石上来倾听各位的心声了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个猪头放他们进来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位恐怖份子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊？无礼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦多尔·石上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早想会会你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是在电视上抨击我和雪之的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会了解个中缘由的 遥·阿米蒂奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到非常的悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟让如此野蛮暴力的人担任国政要职
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你更让人恼火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克利斯德和阿米蒂奇是艾尔里斯的智慧与灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚吧 怪帽男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 会下去才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为何我能平静地忍受这么多耻笑谩骂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗？遥·阿米蒂奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…交到女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 正因有爱 我才能超越一切困难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 为了爱 我才决定成为世界的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的这份情意要向全艾尔里斯国民…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说他原来是给人画像的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 首先允许我向全世界介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久将会成为这个国家第一夫人的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MY SWEET HONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不机灵的男人还真是讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友绘·玛格丽特？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是Valkyrie部队的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个带着玩乐心态出卖同伴的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一夫人？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亲手埋葬石上之后的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是新的 总统候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友绘 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 投给我神圣一票 并接受我的支配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 不要随便在那边起哄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适可而止的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的脑袋可就要开花了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是艾尔里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂 准将 千绘学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔 艾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别被任何人察觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister梦宫·艾利卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真是幸运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我放弃做家事跑出来是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 劫巴士的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们仔细看看那个奇装异服的蚂蚁头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的确 好像是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小行星粉碎者艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是什么大不了的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还真不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 快把那些家伙干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白不见了 我现在无法使用乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你再次成为我们的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 人质是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的孩子怎么都这么笨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚睡醒的时候 谁都是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是活该 梦宫·艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我在家观赏电视直播咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那是 友绘？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾尔里斯共和国大总统雪之·克利斯德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来与你们直接交涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你上巴士来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我就愿意和你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 请将人质全数释放
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 准将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把那孩子也放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:11:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她是最妨碍大公殿下的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔里斯不会向恐怖分子屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你们还会成为风花王国的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶说过打女人的男人最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 雪之小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡才是 很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想亲自找到真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小遥失踪的话 我也会想这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我必须不是大总统才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之小姐你 不会和准将吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会啊 经常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和小遥之间 有一个规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规矩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我错了 小遥会斥责我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她错了 我也要斥责她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后两人好好地谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找出双方都认为正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就毫不犹豫地沿着它走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乃五柱之一 银河之蓝玉莎拉·盖勒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求代理系统认证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物质化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小遥她一定会去做我认为正确的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥·阿米蒂奇准将
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪 开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挟持人质 还想威胁我们释放凪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想藉助他人之力的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠自己的力量 堂堂正正对决
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是奴兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认对象为敌对生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将 雪之小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥·阿米蒂奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有珠洲之黄玉的乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名将汝之力量释放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 准将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵从大统领的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我不把你打成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去避难 克利斯德阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你 Meister莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 您看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白之金刚石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖之Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三·姫野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta队型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖才不会袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来揭穿你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要粘我到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你可不要穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搞背后偷袭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0003,,{\fad(450,0)\fs17}艾尔里斯境内\N戴斯普利特监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能得到释放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正跟那种挟持巴士的蠢货逃走 也会马上被抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料果然失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人鄙夷的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该称赞我聪明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有三餐还有午觉 我还满中意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不像在黑之谷需要劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 谷里发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之谷消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白和舞衣也跟着消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我 凪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说“他”来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说是“她”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到加尔德罗贝来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招的乙HiME们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳米机器被石化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但全身变成矿物一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的只是一小部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我在阿尔泰遗迹里找到的文献里得知的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0014,,{\fad(450,450)\fs17}阿尔泰公国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,0)\fs19}条纹小站
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在条纹团的据点 一副Meister的装束行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今说这些干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些政府官员有事的话 让他们来这里找就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么和平维护者 和小混混没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 之前说的那东西呢 小山田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我小山田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真打算去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是别无他法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从回到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依旧那么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物也油腻得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因为厌恶这里 才去加尔德罗贝的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是被降职了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想扳回一城…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我不是很赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说 你们五柱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.67,0:23:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 小山田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister朱莉叶·奈绪·张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将客人带到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 奈绪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.00,0:25:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(300,300)\move(230,190,400,190)}是老虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.80,0:25:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(300,300)\move(400,250,300,250)}你要成为老虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.51,0:25:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,那么 你找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.40,0:25:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(300,300)\move(180,150,180,230)\fn@simhei\frz-90}换上最后的舞斗服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,叫你来做个下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.44,0:25:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,就为了这个把我叫来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.00,0:25:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(300,300)\pos(280,200)\fn@simhei\frz-90}乙HiME们的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.95,0:25:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.71,0:25:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,莎拉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.70,0:25:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(300,300)\move(400,200,330,230)}热战即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.93,0:25:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,你们根本就不懂怎么做预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.61,0:25:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,让我示范给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.89,0:26:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,你想做就请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.18,0:26:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(100,0)}待续？{\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.33,0:26:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,那么 下回是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.54,0:26:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(550,394)}条纹舞／少女的迷宫


